The Breast Start App will help you find support locally and nationally, get your baby breastfeeding, solve problems, teach you to hand express, offer you rewards, guide you to local breastfeeding friendly places and much, much more!The Breast Start App has â2 clicksâ to a solution and aims to help you anytime, anywhere.The Breast Start App is designed to be breastfeeding parent friendly, with links to web pages that have been approved by an NHS breastfeeding specialist.
